OL,3,CAbortion: What are safe access zones
OL,4,Cand is silent prayer banned?
OL,6,FSo-called buffer zones outside
OL,7,Fabortion clinics across England and
OL,8,FWales are now in place.
OL,10,FSilent prayer, which has been a point
OL,11,Fof contention, is not an automatic
OL,12,Foffence but people doing this within
OL,13,Fthe zones could be liable for
OL,14,Fprosecution, according to new guidance.
OL,16,FHere, ITV News explains what the new
OL,17,Fzones are and what enforcement
OL,18,Fmeasures will be in place.
OL,20,FWhat is a buffer zone?
