OL,3,CAbortion: What are safe access zones
OL,4,Cand is silent prayer banned?
OL,6,FKnown as "safe access zones" in the
OL,7,Flegislation, these are areas within
OL,8,F150 metres of a clinic or hospital
OL,9,Fproviding abortion services.
OL,11,FUnder the Public Order Act 2023, it is
OL,12,Fan offence for someone to, within this
OL,13,Farea, do anything that intentionally
OL,14,For recklessly influences someone's
OL,15,Fdecision to use abortion services,
OL,16,Fobstructs them, or causes harassment,
OL,17,Falarm or distress to someone using or
OL,18,Fworking at the premises.
OL,20,FAnyone found guilty of such an offence
OL,21,Fwill face an unlimited fine.
