OL,6,FWhere does this apply?
OL,8,FEngland and Wales.
OL,10,FLegislation creating buffer zones
OL,11,Faround abortion clinics in Scotland,
OL,12,Fbanning any protests or vigils there,
OL,13,Fcame into force last month.
OL,15,FIn Northern Ireland, safe access zones
OL,16,Fat health service locations which
OL,17,Foffer abortion and birth control
OL,18,Fservices have been in place since
OL,19,FSeptember 2023.
