OL,3,CAbortion: What are safe access zones
OL,4,Cand is silent prayer banned?
OL,6,FKnown as public spaces protection
OL,7,Forders (PSPOs), the first in the UK
OL,8,Fwas enacted by Ealing Council in west
OL,9,FLondon in April 2018, outside the MSI
OL,10,FReproductive Choices Clinic in Mattock
OL,11,FLane.
OL,13,FCampaigners had long made the case for
OL,14,Fthe need for national legislation,
OL,15,Farguing that PSPOs depend on local
OL,16,Fcouncils' willingness, are timebound,
OL,17,Fcan be expensive and result in a
OL,18,Fpostcode lottery.
