OL,3,CAbortion: What are safe access zones
OL,4,Cand is silent prayer banned?
OL,6,FAs it is the Public Order Act 2023,
OL,7,Fwhy have the zones only come into
OL,8,Feffect from October 31, 2024?
OL,10,FThe Bill ` which on the whole is aimed
OL,11,Fat curbing guerrilla protest tactics
OL,12,Fused by groups such as Just Stop Oil
OL,13,Fand Extinction Rebellion ` received
OL,14,Froyal assent on May 2, 2023, becoming
OL,15,Flaw.
OL,17,FBut in December the then-Conservative
OL,18,Fgovernment launched a consultation
OL,19,Finto non-statutory guidance around the
OL,20,Fenforcement of the safe access zones.
