OL,3,CAbortion: What are safe access zones
OL,4,Cand is silent prayer banned?
OL,6,FThat guidance suggested prayer within
OL,7,Fsuch a zone "should not automatically
OL,8,Fbe seen as unlawful", and that silent
OL,9,Fprayer "is protected as an absolute
OL,10,Fright under the Human Rights Act 1998".
OL,12,FWhy has silent prayer has been a
OL,13,Fsticking point?
OL,15,FPro-choice campaigners argued that the
OL,16,Fdraft guidance did not reflect the
OL,17,Fdebate in Parliament.
OL,19,FMPs had in March 2023 rejected
OL,20,Fattempts to allow silent prayer in the
OL,21,Fzones.
