OL,3,CAbortion: What are safe access zones
OL,4,Cand is silent prayer banned?
OL,6,FA group of Tory and DUP MPs had tabled
OL,7,Fan amendment aimed at ensuring no
OL,8,Foffence is committed if a person is
OL,9,F"engaged in consensual communication
OL,10,For in silent prayer" outside clinics
OL,11,For hospitals offering abortion
OL,12,Fservices.
OL,14,FThey argued that this section of the
OL,15,FBill was "leading us into the
OL,16,Fterritory of thought crimes", while
OL,17,Fone MP described it as "dystopian".
OL,19,FBut, in a free vote, the proposal was
OL,20,Frejected by 116 votes to 299 - a
OL,21,Fmajority of 183.
