OL,6,FWhat is the new guidance?
OL,8,FThe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,9,Fhas published guidance to prosecutors
OL,10,Fstating there is no defence on
OL,11,Freligious or ethical grounds to people
OL,12,Fseeking to influence, obstruct or
OL,13,Fcause harassment to others within safe
OL,14,Faccess zones.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
