OL,3,CAbortion: What are safe access zones
OL,4,Cand is silent prayer banned?
OL,6,FThe College of Policing has published
OL,7,Fwhat it described as a "brief" for
OL,8,Fofficers on Section 9 of the Act,
OL,9,Fwhich deals with safe access zones.
OL,11,FIt states: "All decisions must be made
OL,12,Fon a case-by-case basis and must be
OL,13,Fbalanced and proportionate to the
OL,14,Fcircumstances."
OL,16,FThe Home Office said the guidance will
OL,17,F"ensure there is clarity and
OL,18,Fconsistency with the enforcement of
OL,19,Fthe new offence".
