OL,3,CAbortion: What are safe access zones
OL,4,Cand is silent prayer banned?
OL,6,FAre the zones being marked out in some
OL,7,Fway?
OL,9,FThere is no requirement within the
OL,10,Flegislation for the zones to be marked
OL,11,Fout.
OL,13,FThe person suspected of an offence
OL,14,Fdoes not have to know or believe they
OL,15,Fare in a safe access zone, the CPS
OL,16,Fguidance states.
OL,18,FIt is understood local police forces
OL,19,Fwill work with clinics to decide
OL,20,Fwhether signage marking out the zones
OL,21,Fwould be helpful or not.
